
## The Last Billionaire

Le dernier milliardaire (English title: The Last Billionaire) is a 1934 French comedy film directed by René Clair and starring Max Dearly, Marthe Mellot and Renée Saint-Cyr. The film is based on a fictional small European kingdom which is on the verge of going broke.

# Cast 

Max Dearly - Banco
Marthe Mellot - Queen of Casinario
Renée Saint-Cyr - Princess Isabelle
Sinoël - Prime Minister
Charles Redgie - Crown Prince Nicolas
Marcel Carpentier - Detective Brown
Raymond Cordy - Valet
José Noguero - Bandleader
Ray Romano - Co-director

